      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，bottom-to-top布局。那主干main需要先有两个初始commit，然后再分叉对吧？两个分支分别叫feature-001和feature-002？",
      "elements_involved": [
